  "2026-04-07T08:42:17.148Z",codex-agent,"Completed Wave 8/9 test-all blast-radius controls: added --limit/--offset filtering before linked-test execution while preserving deterministic ID ordering and existing status filtering semantics. Wired new flags through main CLI command parsing, managed background command argument forwarding, contracts/schema, completion (bash/zsh/fish), Pi wrapper mapping, and help examples. Added runtime validation for non-negative integer limit/offset plus pagination regression coverage and help/contracts parity tests. Verification passed: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/test-all-command.spec.ts tests/unit/completion-command.spec.ts tests/unit/contracts-command.spec.ts tests/unit/pi-agent-extension.spec.ts tests/integration/release-readiness-runtime.spec.ts."
